@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gopirc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.abs(v0) * wp.exp(wp.exp(tmp + 0.32)))
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.exp(wp.cos(v2 + 0.53)))
    v0 = wp.exp(0.50)
    v1 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.42 - tmp + 0.69)) - (wp.abs(v1 + 0.26) * v2))
    v2 = 0.71
    data[tid] = v0
